summary: The critical render loop was stopped by stabilizing study action callbacks and making lesson-open writes once-per-day, the service worker now respects the update banner instead of auto-activating on install, the study review flow is protected against double taps, scroll restoration is wired into router navigation, and missing card or lesson IDs now fail safely; the requested commit was created, but a separate post-commit worktree change appeared and is called out above.
